race.description: Mcqueens Tavern (Queens) Grade 5 Series H Cta Divi
race.comment: PRINCESS TILLEY (1) was below best last time at this track (30.98) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length sixth. Has already won three times from this draw. Makes strong appeal on best. PARRAKIE (3) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 530m behind Talbot Road (31.34) in a Grade 5. Worth following up. LINKIN GIRL (6) was a strong course and distance winner last time, claiming a Invitation in a powerful 30.92 and a new PB here. Top win latest and can measure up again. HEY YOU GUYS (8) placed in slick time last start - worth some thought.
